 [derived]","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":"- Call and put are terms derived from the longs and shorts.\r\n\r\n- A call is an option to buy (that is, a\r\nlong contract),"},{"id":"id-968443ce","name":"put [derived]","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":"put is an option to sell (a short contract)."},{"id":"id-6d365bab","name":"delivery date","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":"Without considering holidays,\r\nwe can determine the delivery date by a simple calculation between date and\r\ntenor"},{"id":"id-4be02016","name":"product","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":"The key difference between a product and a contract is that the product\r\nrepresents the customer's intention while the contract refers to what actually gets\r\ntraded between the counter and primary parties"},{"id":"d8bbe40b","name":"party","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":""},{"id":"id-2169dbcc","name":"combination product","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":"- combination options can be seen as a composite of other options."},{"id":"id-3c435f9e","name":"risk reversal","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":""},{"id":"id-04e54c01","name":"strangle","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":""},{"id":"id-7c7c2eba","name":"spread","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":"-  spread is two\r\noptions, but both options are the same direction (that is, two calls or two puts)\r\nat different prices."},{"id":"dd0aee7b","name":"straddle","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":"- straddles двойной опцион"},{"id":"id-888f2521","name":"call spread","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":""},{"id":"id-2a2f9499","name":"put spread","type":"BusinessObject","layer":"business","documentation":""},{"id":"id-44ad9d93","name":"spot<barrier,  classify as knocked-in","type":"Business